      <!-- What We Do -->
      <div class="about_us_section">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 grey_back">
               <h2>What We Do at Nature's Flavors</h2>
               <p>For over 40 years, we have been developing and producing custom flavors and <%= link_to "fragrances", (Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Fragrances").present? ? seo_url(Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Fragrances")): '/')  %> for both consumers and businesses.</p>
               <p>Our skilled flavorists at Nature's Flavors use only the highest quality natural ingredients, sourced from around the world, to construct our <%= link_to "extracts & flavorings", (Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Extracts & Flavorings").present? ? seo_url(Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Extracts & Flavorings")): '/')  %>, flavor oils, <%= link_to "syrups", (Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Syrups").present? ? seo_url(Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Syrups")): '/')  %>, and fragrances.</p>
               <p>All of our <%= link_to "natural flavorings oils", (Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Natural Flavor Oil").present? ? seo_url(Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Natural Flavor Oil")): '/')  %>, <%= link_to "flavor concentrates", (Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Flavor Concentrates").present? ? seo_url(Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Flavor Concentrates")): '/')  %>, extracts, citric acids, and fragrances are used to enhance, maintain, or improve the taste, aroma, color, and flavor of goods.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 mobile-hide"><%= image_tag "about-us/lemonade.jpg", alt:"Natural Lemonade Syrup" %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
